                        <title key="work_11808">Fasciculus morum</title>
                        <rubric>Tractatus de Viciis &amp; Virtutibus qui Fasciculus Morum nominatur</rubric>
                        <note>Etenim habetur in regula beati Francisci'. Part of fol. 126 is torn away.</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem class="#tabulae">
                        <note> At fol. 218v is an appendix of 'Sermones in libro qui intitulatur Fasciculus morum', after which comes the index.</note>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="#theologica" n="3" xml:id="MS_Bodl_187-item3">
